ummer-jay-weinberg-3569424">Slipknot</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/liam-and-noel-gallagher-have-been-turned-into-funko-pop-figures-3261306">Liam 和 Noel Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-these-new-white-stripes-funko-pop-figures-3180554">The White Stripes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/metallica-announce-new-funko-pop-figures-to-celebrate-the-black-album-3060272">Metallica</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/can-now-post-malone-funko-pop-doll-2449837">Post Malone</a>和已故的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eddie-van-halen-set-to-be-honoured-with-new-funko-pop-figure-3117662">Eddie Van Halen</a>等音乐人之后，他成为最新一位获此殊荣的音乐人物。</p><p>弗拉夫不拘一格的 2024 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flavor-flav-names-favourite-taylor-swift-song-declares-himself-king-swiftie-3569578">已经让他成为了一名 Swiftie</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flavor-flav-set-to-star-in-new-reality-show-about-him-going-back-to-high-school-3603535">宣布了一个新的真人秀节目，他将在其中获得高中文凭</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flavor-flav-orders-whole-red-lobster-menu-in-efforts-to-save-chain-restaurant-3763438">订购一份完整的红龙虾菜单来拯救一家海鲜餐厅</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flavor-flav-reveals-the-custom-bronze-clock-hes-had-made-for-olympic-gymnast-jordan-chiles-3783474">Flavor Flav 的帖子展示了他为奥运会体操运动员乔丹·奇利斯 (Jordan Chiles) 制作的定制青铜钟，该钟</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
